      },
      "date": "2013-01-18 11:27:41.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: (3 inline comments)\n\nCan you please submit a new patch to remove the emacs 4-space tabs line from sanity.sh that was added by this patch.\n\nIt would also be great if you could look into build/checkpatch.pl to see why it doesn't complain about spaces used for indentation in shell scripts, since casual inspection of that script shows it _should_ be checking the style of .sh files as well as .c and .h files.  That would have caught this issue much earlier.",
